  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the addition of an interdental cleaning device paired with a manual
      toothbrush compared to using a manual toothbrush only. Plaque removal, reduction of gingival
      bleeding and reduction of gingival inflammation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
